subject: Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Wayne Ellington had 17 points and his fellow freshman Brandan Wright added 16 to lead No. 7 North Carolina to a 75-63 victory over Kentucky yesterday in Chapel Hill, N.C., in a game between college basketball’s two programs with the most wins.
